# Panini Finance Core

## Glassbox mandate

**All problems will be solved as glassbox.**

Every problem (notes examples, Glassbox Math tab, Practice MCQ solutions) must expose:
1. First principle / accounting identity
2. Numbered derivation steps with formulas
3. Statement flow (what hits NI, OCI, assets, equity, cash)
4. IFRS vs US GAAP when relevant
5. Final answer + quick sanity check

## Repo map

- `src/data/curriculum.js` — topics / LM status
- `src/data/lm##_*.js` — module content
- `src/App.jsx` — `MODULE_CONTENT` registry + UI
- `noupload/` — local only; never commit (see `.gitignore`)

## When adding an LM

Follow `.cursor/skills/add-cfa-module/SKILL.md` and `.cursor/skills/glassbox-problems/SKILL.md`.
